sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Python as [Python Package]
  participant Backend as [Backend]
  participant DB as [DB]
  participant Redis as [Redis]
  participant MTX as [MediaMTX :8888]

  opt capability check
    Python->>Backend: GET /api/v1/info
    Note over Python,Backend: Auth 불필요<br/>Python package는 capabilities.live_streams를 확인한다.<br/>HLS playback URL 구성에는 info.urls.hls_port를 사용하지 않고 fixed 8888을 사용한다.
    Backend-->>Python: 200 server info
  end

  Python->>Backend: GET /api/v1/live-streams
  Note over Python,Backend: Headers<br/>Authorization: Bearer ef_raw_python_static_token

  Backend->>Backend: requireDashboardOrAppOrPython
  Backend->>DB: readable repository ids 계산
  Note over Backend,DB: admin은 전체 repository read 가능<br/>일반 사용자는 repo_members와 public repository 기준

  Backend->>Redis: active stream cache 조회
  Note over Backend,Redis: set: stream:active:sessions<br/>MGET: stream:recording:{recordingSessionId}<br/><br/>목록 응답에는 HTTP upload progress fields를 포함하지 않는다.

  Backend-->>Python: 200 { streams }
  Note over Backend,Python: stream item fields<br/>recording_session_id<br/>repository_id<br/>repository_name<br/>user_id<br/>device_type<br/>ingest_type<br/>stream_path<br/>status=live<br/>playback_available

  Python->>Python: playback 대상 stream 선택
  Note over Python: selector는 LiveStreamInfo, recording_session_id, stream_path, repository_name을 사용할 수 있다.<br/>HLS playback 대상은 ingest_type=MEDIAMTX이고 playback_available=true인 stream이다.

  alt selected stream lacks playback detail
    Python->>Backend: GET /api/v1/live-streams/{recordingSessionId}
    Note over Python,Backend: Headers<br/>Authorization: Bearer ef_raw_python_static_token
    Backend->>DB: STREAMING session + repository read 권한 확인
    Backend->>MTX: active path 조회
    Note over Backend,MTX: MediaMTX Control API로 path active 여부 확인
    Backend-->>Python: 200 stream detail
    Note over Backend,Python: detail fields<br/>recording_session_id<br/>repository_id<br/>repository_name<br/>owner_id<br/>user_id<br/>device_type<br/>ingest_type<br/>stream_path<br/>registered_at<br/>status=live<br/>playback_available<br/>playback_ready<br/>bytes_received: number | null<br/>last_sequence: number | null<br/>last_chunk_at: ISO datetime | null
  end

  alt not playable
    Python->>Python: raise EgoFlowStreamError
    Note over Python: ingest_type != MEDIAMTX<br/>or playback_available=false<br/>or playback_ready is not true<br/>or stream_path missing
  else playable
    Python->>Backend: GET /api/v1/auth/python/tokens/validate
    Note over Python,Backend: Headers<br/>Authorization: Bearer ef_raw_python_static_token
    Backend->>Backend: requirePythonToken
    Backend->>DB: active API token owner 조회
    Backend-->>Python: 200 { valid: true, user: { id, role, display_name } }
    Note over Python: Python package는 user.id를 viewer_user_id로 cache한다.

    Python->>Backend: POST /api/v1/live-streams/{recordingSessionId}/playback-ticket
    Note over Python,Backend: Headers<br/>Authorization: Bearer ef_raw_python_static_token<br/>Body 없음

    Backend->>Backend: requireDashboardOrPython
    Backend->>Redis: live cache 확인
    Note over Backend,Redis: key: stream:recording:{recordingSessionId}<br/>required status=STREAMING and MEDIAMTX live session
    Backend->>DB: repository read 권한 확인

    alt stream hidden or not playable
      Backend-->>Python: 404 Not Found or 409 Conflict
    else ticket issued
      Backend->>Redis: playback ticket 저장
      Note over Backend,Redis: key: stream:hls-ticket:{playbackTicket}<br/><br/>value fields<br/>recordingSessionId<br/>repositoryId<br/>userId<br/>ingestType=MEDIAMTX<br/>streamPath<br/>status=active<br/><br/>TTL: 600 seconds
      Backend-->>Python: 201 { playback_ticket }
    end

    Python->>Python: direct HLS URL 구성
    Note over Python: host = URL(api_base_url).hostname<br/>port = fixed 8888<br/>url = http://{host}:8888/{stream_path}/index.m3u8?ticket={playback_ticket}&user_id={viewer_user_id}

    Python->>MTX: GET /live/{repo}/{recordingSessionId}/index.m3u8?ticket=pt_...&user_id=viewer
    Note over Python,MTX: Authorization header는 사용하지 않는다.<br/>HLS bytes는 Caddy를 거치지 않고 MediaMTX 8888/tcp에서 직접 받는다.

    MTX->>Backend: POST /api/v1/auth/mediamtx
    Note over MTX,Backend: MediaMTX authHTTPAddress payload<br/>action=read<br/>protocol=hls<br/>path=live/{repo}/{recordingSessionId}<br/>query=ticket=pt_...&user_id=viewer

    Backend->>Redis: playback ticket + live cache 검증
    Note over Backend,Redis: DB-free hot path<br/>1. stream:hls-ticket:{ticket} exists<br/>2. ticket.status=active<br/>3. ticket.userId == query.user_id<br/>4. ticket.streamPath == path<br/>5. stream:recording:{recordingSessionId} exists<br/>6. live cache status=STREAMING<br/>7. repositoryId/path match<br/>8. ticket TTL refresh to 600s

    alt ticket invalid or stream inactive
      Backend-->>MTX: 401 Unauthorized
      MTX-->>Python: HLS request rejected
    else ticket valid
      Backend-->>MTX: 200 OK
      MTX-->>Python: playlist or fMP4 segment bytes
    end

    loop while playback continues
      Python->>MTX: media playlist / fMP4 segment request
      MTX->>Backend: POST /api/v1/auth/mediamtx
      Backend->>Redis: Redis-only validation + TTL refresh
      Backend-->>MTX: 200 OK
      MTX-->>Python: playlist or fMP4 bytes
    end
  end

%% 참고:
%% Python package는 Dashboard에서 발급받은 ef_ static token만 사용한다.
%% Python package는 HLS direct URL을 구성할 때 server info의 hls_port를 사용하지 않고 fixed 8888을 사용한다.
%% Python package는 playback-ticket 발급 전에 /auth/python/tokens/validate로 viewer user id를 얻고 cache한다.
%% HLS URL query는 ticket과 user_id만 사용한다. Authorization header는 HLS playlist/segment 요청에 붙이지 않는다.
%% Python HLS client가 segment request까지 query를 유지하지 않으면 각 playlist/segment URL에 같은 query를 다시 붙여야 한다.
%% HTTP ingest stream은 live list에는 보이지만 Python HLS playback 대상으로 열지 않는다.
%% 이 문서는 Python package 관점의 live playback 흐름이다. 공통 HLS playback 구조는 .mermaid/PLAYBACK/python-hls-playback.mmd도 참고한다.
